## Key Features Implemented

### Authentication System
- ✅ Unified login for all roles (Admin, Company, Student)
- ✅ Company registration with pending approval status
- ✅ Student self-registration
- ✅ Pre-existing admin user (admin@portal.com / admin123)
- ✅ Flask-Login session management
- ✅ Role-based access control with custom decorators

### Admin Functionalities
- ✅ Dashboard with statistics (students, companies, drives, applications)
- ✅ Approve/Reject company registrations
- ✅ Approve/Reject placement drives
- ✅ Search students by name, roll number, or phone
- ✅ Search companies by name
- ✅ Edit student profiles
- ✅ Blacklist/Unblacklist students and companies
- ✅ Delete students and companies

### Company Functionalities
- ✅ Company registration with approval workflow
- ✅ Cannot login until approved by admin
- ✅ Company dashboard with stats
- ✅ Create placement drives (pending approval)
- ✅ Edit/Close/Delete placement drives
- ✅ View applications per drive
- ✅ Update application status (Shortlisted/Selected/Rejected)

### Student Functionalities
- ✅ Student registration and login
- ✅ Profile management with CGPA, branch, resume URL
- ✅ View only approved placement drives
- ✅ Apply to placement drives
- ✅ CGPA eligibility check before applying
- ✅ Prevent duplicate applications
- ✅ Application history with status tracking

### Core Business Logic
- ✅ Only approved companies can create drives
- ✅ Only approved drives visible to students
- ✅ Duplicate application prevention (unique constraint)
- ✅ CGPA-based eligibility validation
- ✅ Blacklist enforcement for companies and students

