## Database Schema

| Table | Description |
|-------|-------------|
| **users** | Base authentication (id, email, password_hash, role, is_active) |
| **students** | Student profiles (user_id, name, roll_number, branch, cgpa, etc.) |
| **companies** | Company profiles (user_id, name, hr_contact, approval_status, etc.) |
| **placement_drives** | Job postings (company_id, job_title, min_cgpa, package, deadline, status) |
| **applications** | Student applications (student_id, drive_id, status, applied_at) |

